# Harness Workflow Conventions

## Task State

- All task state lives in `.agents/tasks/task-NNN/`
- Plan: `plan.md`, Build logs: `build-rN.log`, Evaluations: `evaluation-rN.md`
- Never delete task artifacts — they form the audit trail

## Commit Format

Use conventional commits: `<type>(scope): description`
- feat: new feature
- fix: bug fix
- refactor: code restructuring
- test: adding or updating tests
- docs: documentation changes
- chore: maintenance tasks

## Branch Convention

- Feature branches: `agent/<task-id>-<short-desc>`
- Trunk branch: `main`
- Never commit directly to trunk
